{"tid":2217552,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰術討論］Partey Welcome to Chelsea","createTime":"2020-09-25T13:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T08:26:21.000Z","uid":167278,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e73d62d4f9acf545b003f7973c01d5c1aed46f17","tid":2217552,"uid":167278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大膽假設：<br />\n<br />\n如果車仔買唔到Rice<br />\n會去買馬體會Partey<br />\n而馬體會會借/買咗阿仙奴嘅Torreria先放Partey<br />\n最後車仔會放Jorginho 去阿仙奴去完成以上轉會操作<br />\n<br />\n最主要原因係車仔Jorginho 拍住Kante 中場防守性低, 中場效率低, 詳細資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.goal.com/en/news/how-arsenal-target-partey-could-solve-chelseas-midfield/8xbbla6a80mp1u3zrawtgfs5b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fhow-arsenal-target-partey-could-solve-chelseas-midfield%2F8xbbla6a80mp1u3zrawtgfs5b&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=3cf4c613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.goal.com/en/news/how-arsenal-target-partey-could-solve-chelseas-midfield/8xbbla6a80mp1u3zrawtgfs5b</a><br />\n<br />\nInterestingly, what Jorginho and Kante lack in their skill-set, Partey possesses in his repertoire.<br />\n簡單來講Partey 係Jorginho 同Kante 合成體<br />\n<br />\nPartey / Rice 配 Kante <br />\n先可以用盡Kante 優勢去解放前場進攻火力<br />\n而Partey 係帶波上前場效果上又比Jorginho 好得多<br />\n<br />\nJorginho 嘅最大用途係後場build-up play <br />\n現時車仔應該更加傾向將個波俾前場build up attack <br />\n姐係玩番Lampard Ballack Makelele個時嘅433<br />\n<br />\n所以呢個連鎖轉會系列<br />\n我個人都覺得係三方都贏嘅局面<br />\n機會性幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.fanpiece.com/m/chelseahk-ktbffh/c1382161.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fchelseahk-ktbffh%2Fc1382161.html&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=d4202037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://football.fanpiece.com/m/chelseahk-ktbffh/c1382161.html</a><br />\nJorginho 可能係達蛇復興路上最後一塊拼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2669d45c7b88da51d47f4ed6353f2280bdcde9fe","tid":2217552,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"明明我廠都想要派對，依家要硬食舒服？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32718b5c8f6e00aed1cc7a5d30008615054e60ac","tid":2217552,"uid":167278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"舒服岩用過派對<br />\n有得硬食又唔拘喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c203a49b475fac07792fecbab1fd5a84abc568","tid":2217552,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32718b5c8f6e00aed1cc7a5d30008615054e60ac","tid":2217552,"uid":167278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"舒服岩用過派對<br />\n有得硬食又唔拘喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"屌，咁你車慢慢舒服啦，咪爭派對唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb1dc770d3a3d2be719d2f59faaef00d797d0db","tid":2217552,"uid":167278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T08:26:21.000Z","msg":"Jorginho 無速度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/thearsenalrevo1/status/1311952422122684417?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthearsenalrevo1%2Fstatus%2F1311952422122684417%3Fs%3D21&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=ef8a44a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fthearsenalrevo1%2Fstatus%2F1311952422122684417%3Fs%3D21&h=b65b7aae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/thearsenalrevo1/status/1311952422122684417?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nJorginho 無個人防守能力<br />\n<br />\n<a href